\chapter{Store}

The store is where the design stops being a pure document generator and becomes
a persistent polling system.  It has three jobs:
\begin{description}
\item[Configuration] locate the shared configuration file in a way that works
  both from the CLI and from PythonTeX,
\item[Registration] assign stable URL prefixes to questions, and
\item[Persistence] append answers with an atomic rewrite so a half-written file
  never replaces a valid one.
\end{description}

